<div style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #222;">
  <p>Hello <strong><%= @tenant.full_name %></strong>,</p>
  <p>This is a friendly reminder that your rent invoice is due on <strong><%= @invoice.due_on %></strong>.</p>
  <p>
    <strong>Amount due:</strong>
    <span style="font-size: 18px;">
      <%= sprintf('%.2f', @invoice.balance_cents / 100.0) %> <%= @invoice.currency %>
    </span>
  </p>
  <p>Please make the payment at your earliest convenience. If you've already paid, please disregard this message.</p>
  <p>Thank you,<br/>Franco Property Management</p>
</div>
